data type ix

pandas, indexing and selecting data


.iloc, .loc, .ix




.iloc
> able to find the value by 'integer position', but cannot be done by 'label'.

.loc
> able to find the value by 'label', but cannot be done by 'integer position'.

.ix
> able to use both integer position and label to find certain value. 
> If the label is an integer, only label-based index works.



